snippet.title: Mowgli Teaser | Roshan Kanakala | Sandeep Raj | Bandi Saroj Kumar | Sakkshi | TG Vishwa Prasad | PMF
snippet.description:
Mowgli is an upcoming unique romantic action drama set deep within a forest backdrop. Directed by National Award-winning filmmaker Sandeep Raj (Colour Photo), Produced by TG Vishwa Prasad and Krithi Prasad under People Media Factory Banner.The film has cinematography by Rama Maruthi M, while Kaala Bhairava scores the music. The work is co-written by Rama Maruthi M and Radhakrishna Reddy The technical team also includes Peekay as editor, Kiran Mamidi as art director, and Natraj Madigonda choreographing the action sequences.

Mowgli 2025 will arrive in cinemas on December 12th, 2025.

Cast: Roshan Kanakala, Sakkshi Mhadolkar, Bandi Saroj Kumar & Harsha Chemudu

Technical Crew:
Writer & Director: Sandeep Raj
Producers: TG Vishwa Prasad, Krithi Prasad
Banner: People Media Factory
Music: Kaala Bhairava
DOP: Rama Maruti M
Editor: Peekay 
Art: Kiran Mamidi

snippet.title: Man Vs Baby | Official Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
After a job looking after a high-tech mansion ended in disaster thanks to an irritating insect in Man vs Bee, Trevor Bingley (Rowan Atkinson) has left the stressful world of housesitting for the quieter life of a school caretaker. That is, until a lucrative offer to look after a luxury London penthouse over Christmas proves too tempting to resist. But on the last day of term, when no one comes to collect the Baby Jesus from the school nativity, Trevor finds himself with another undersized and very unexpected companion. With a penthouse to protect and a baby to burp, will Trevor be able to have the calm Christmas he hopes for, or will festivities descend into chaos?

Watch on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/title/81516058

snippet.title: The Family Man S3 - Official Trailer | Raj & DK | Manoj Bajpayee, Jaideep Ahlawat | Prime Video IN
snippet.description:
Prime Video India Presents
The Family Man Season 3 Official Trailer 

SERIES:
"The Family Man," created by Raj & DK, an edgy and thrilling series on Prime Video, follows the life of Srikant Tiwari, a seemingly ordinary middle-class man who secretly works for the Threat Assessment and Surveillance Cell( TASC), a fictional cell of the National Investigation Agency in Mumbai. Balancing the demands of his high-stakes job and his family, life proves increasingly challenging as Srikant navigates dangerous missions against terrorists while trying to be a present husband and father. snippet.title: The Devil Wears Prada 2 | Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
A sequel? For spring? Groundbreaking. Meryl Streep, Anne Hathaway, Emily Blunt, and Stanley Tucci return in The Devil Wears Prada 2, in theaters May 1, 2026. Watch the teaser trailer now.¬†

Almost twenty years after making their iconic turns as Miranda, Andy, Emily and Nigel‚ÄîMeryl Streep, Anne Hathaway, Emily Blunt and Stanley Tucci return to the fashionable streets of New York City and the sleek offices of Runway Magazine in the eagerly awaited sequel to the 2006 phenomenon that defined a generation. 
 
The film reunites the original main cast with director David Frankel and writer Aline Brosh McKenna, and introduces an all-new runway of characters including Kenneth Branagh, Simone Ashley, Justin Theroux, Lucy Liu, Patrick Brammall, Caleb Hearon, Helen J. Shen, Pauline Chalamet, B.J. Novak and Conrad Ricamora. Tracie Thoms and Tibor Feldman also reprise their roles as ‚ÄúLily‚Äù and ‚ÄúIrv‚Äù from the first film. 
 
‚ÄúThe Devil Wears Prada 2‚Äù is produced by Wendy Finerman, and executive produced by Michael Bederman, Karen Rosenfelt and McKenna. The film debuts exclusively in theaters May 1, 2026.

Aa jaaye yahan daur koi
Dil mein hamesha tum hi rahoge
Na aayega aur koi 

Hum bas tere hain 
Jab tak jiyenge tere hi rahenge
Hum ye kah rahe hain
Hum toh tere hain tere hi rahenge 

Rasta ek ho tera mera yahan 
Maangta hoon main aur kuch bhi Kahan
Tu mujhe jo mile dard mere hansenge 
Kaash mujhko tu bhi yun hi chaahta 

Haar jaaun kahin toh junoon tu bane
Zindagi bhar ka mere sukoon tu bane 

Ab meri shaamein mere savere
Honge na tere bagair koi 
Dil mein hamesha tum hi rahoge 
Na aayega aur koi 
Hum bas tere hain 
Jab tak jiyenge tere hi rahenge 
Hum ye kah rahe hain 
Hum toh tere hain tere hi rahenge

#HarshvardhanRane #SonamBajwa #DeewaniyatKiDiwali #Diwali2025.

Laxmi Aarti in Hindi,lakshmi aarti,maha lakshmi aarti,‡§≤‡§ï‡•ç‡§∑‡•ç‡§Æ‡•Ä ‡§Ü‡§∞‡§§‡•Ä ‡§π‡§ø‡§Ç‡§¶‡•Ä,‡§≤‡§ï‡•ç‡§∑‡•ç‡§Æ‡•Ä ‡§Ü‡§∞‡§§‡•Ä ‡§π‡§ø‡§Ç‡§¶‡•Ä ‡§Æ‡•á‡§Ç,Om Jai Laxmi Mata,om jai lakshmi mata,jai lakshmi mata aarti,jai laxmi mata,‡§ú‡§Ø ‡§≤‡§ï‡•ç‡§∑‡•ç‡§Æ‡•Ä ‡§Æ‡§æ‡§§‡§æ,‡•ê ‡§ú‡§Ø ‡§≤‡§ï‡•ç‡§∑‡•ç‡§Æ‡•Ä ‡§Æ‡§æ‡§§‡§æ,mahalaxmi songs,om jai laxmi mata,laxmi aarti,laxmi ji ki aarti,lakshmi mata ki aarti,lakshmi ji ki aarti,aarti lakshmi ji ki,aarti laxmi ji ki,laxmi mata ki aarti,laxmi mata aarti,jai laxmi mata aarti,maa laxmi aarti,aarti lakshmi mata ki

Goddess Lakshmi Mata is the goddess of wealth, wisdom, prosperity, grace, generosity and charm. A person who recites this Aarti with true devotion is blessed with wealth and prosperity and a good family life. The worship of Laxmi and the regular chanting of the chalisa is recommended, to those wishing to free their Karma of all the past misdeeds. 

#laxmiaarti #laxmijikiaarti #mahalaxmiaarti #laxmimantra #lakshmiaarti

snippet.title: O Meri Mehbooba Mehbooba Mehbooba (Music Video) - Mohammed Rafi | Dharmendra Hits Songs
snippet.description:
Enjoy the evergreen romantic track ‚ÄúO Meri Mehbooba Mehbooba Mehbooba‚Äù sung by the legendary Mohammed Rafifrom the movie Dharam Veer (1977). Featuring the dynamic Dharmendra and the stunning Zeenat Aman, this melodious song . 

#OMeriMehbooba #MohammedRafi #Dharmendra #ZeenatAman #DharamVeer #LaxmikantPyarelal #BollywoodClassics #EvergreenSongs #OldBollywoodSongs #HindiSongs #BollywoodHits #RomanticSongs 

Credits: 
Singer: Mohammed Rafi
Music: Laxmikant-Pyarelal
Lyrics: Anand Bakshi
Movie: Dharam Veer
Starring: Dharmendra, Zeenat Aman
Director: Manmohan Desai
Producer: Subhash Desai
Label: Universal Music India

Lyrics: 
  
O meri mehbooba mehbooba mehbooba 

tujhey jaana hai toh jaa teri marji mera kya 

par dekh jo tu ruth kar chali jayegi 

tere saath hi mere marne ki khabar aayegi 

O meri mehbooba 

Teri chahat mera chain churaigi 

lekin tujko bhi to nind na ayegi 

main toh mar jaunga leka naam tera 

naam magar kar jaunga badnam tera 

tohba tohba phir kya hoga 

ke yaad mein meri tujko tadapaigi 

tere jaatey hi tere aane ki khabar aayegi 

O meri mehbooba 

Jo bhi meri is prem kahani ka 

par kya hoga teri mast jawani ka 

ashiq hoon main tere dil me raheta hoon 

apni nahin main tere dil ki kaheta hoon 

tohba tohba phir kya hoga 

ke yaad me teri tu pachtaegi 

yeh ruth jawani ki judai main hi guzar jayegi 

O meri mehbooba

snippet.title: Matter (Official Music Video) - Sumit Parta & Panther | New Haryanvi Song 2025
snippet.description:
Presenting new Haryanvi hip hop 2025 ‚Äì Matter by Sumit Parta & Panther

Bringing you the raw and fearless vibe of Haryana with "Matter", the latest fire track by Sumit Parta & Panther.
This song defines real street energy ‚Äî filled with power, attitude, and pride. With intense lyrics, bold delivery, and unstoppable flow, Matter is all about dominance, loyalty, and living with no compromise.

If you believe in your hustle and never back down ‚Äî this one‚Äôs for you. 

Song Credits: 
Song Title: Matter
Singer: Sumit Parta & Panther
Music: Xtacy
Lyricist/Composer: Sumit Parta & Panther

Director: Mohan BeTaab
DOP: Nishan Singh

Distribution By: EYP Consulting
Distribution & Marketing Partner: EYP Creations & Warner Music India
Digitally Managed By: Prince Pannu

Lyrics:
Gaadi Uchi Uchi Rakhe Chale Talke Sedan 
Baat Lambi Koni Khiche Khde Pair Samadhan 
Sath Khaadi Panchgami Kon Gunda Paake Shayami 
Mkha Itni Re Bdi Koni Kise Ki Dukan 

Yaari Dosti Me Sara Ghar Phuk Dewa 
Par Yaari Dosti Me Koni Roli Chalya Kre 
Jiki Nasa Me Se Pani Woye Kre Samjhota 
 Mhare Matter  Me Sun Sidhi Goli Chalya  Kre 

Bair Mhare Chori Sun Dada Layi Chalre H
Gelya Chacha Tau Aale Mere Bhai Chalre H 
Kayi Sale Mere Laan Ki Sakeem Sochre H 
Anty Party Te  Krn Collab Pochre H 

Phle Karam Kand Krya Ib Bnya Hu Me  Singer 
Choro Jaata Ko  Sage Bishnoiya Ka Tinger 
Adhe Shise Khule Bhar Kade Rakhe Chora Finger
5,7 Bhai Paad Dewa Karwayi 
Konya Krke Yo Chora Kathi Toli Chalya Krya 
Jiki Nasa Me Se Pani Woye Kre Samjhota 
Mhare Matter  Me Sun Sidhi Goli Chalya Kre 

Ye Ghoda Chalta Bhi Aur Jalta Bhi
Bas Bhaagta Bhagataa Lekin Peecha Hat-ta Nahi
Ye Ghoda Jeet Dilata Aur Karta Barbaadi
Deta Nahi Maafi Hai Karta Sardari
Aur Faadein Beech Se Gar Bane Koi Jyada Patwari

Raub Jamata Ye Gaddafi Nahi Jhukta Bhale Hi Katta Sir
Mujhe Gaddari Dikhe Minute Se Pehle Got The Vision Of Gandhari
Hoti Mahabharat Tune Buri Nazar Se Dekh Li Gar Meri Panchali
Tere Chacha Bappa Sabki Karwadu Baikunth Tayyari
Aur Sun
Kam Se Jyaada Hai Zubaan Ki Izzat
Aukat Se Jyaada Karte Iman Ki Izzat
Chadhai Se Jyaada Ache Insan Ki
Hum Bhaukal Se Zyaada Karte Ache Khandan Ki Izzat
Gunday Badmash Company Me Jaise Ye Yashraj Ki Picture
Pakke Usool, Lathi Hai Har Sanp Ki Ksimat
Naseeb Me Bheji Bhagwan Ne Pehli Ashiqui Likh Kar
Aur Duji Maut Seene Pe Goli Hath Me Pistol

Hoti Pitayi Lage Kohli Mara Kare
Judge Sab Bole Galat Karam Pe Tere Moti Dhara Lage
Khatey Bikaneri Na Goli Guli Khaya Kare
Panther Bhaiya Jaha Phonchey Og Og Nara Lage

Mkha Kaan Khol Dhyan Te Tu Baat Sun Chooti 
Badmasha Ki Re Koi Prem Khani Konya Hoti 
Tane Mare Subha Shyam Fer  Bole Ga Re Gaam 
Gundya Gelya Link H Flane Ki H Poti 
Karke Ne Kand Kde Bhaje Koni Yaar 
Mhari Sadka Pe Gadi Ye Slowly Chalya Kre 

Jiki Nasa Me Se Pani Woye Kre Samjhota 
Mhare Matter  Me Sun Sidhi Goli Chalya Kre



Stay Tuned & Subscribe/Follow me on:
* Youtube: https://www.youtube.com/c/SumitParta
* Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/sumitparta09/

snippet.title: Bulbul | Muhfaad | Kartavya | 2025
snippet.description:
Music/Mix/Master - Kartavya
Lyrics - Muhfaad 

Bandar chadha pahaad pe karke 
chutadh chaude
chup kyu hai baitha bol sorry behn ke!!

naach meri bulbul milega tujhe paisa
mita du teri chull mile jaise ko taisa
aaye na samajh tujhe izzat ka lehza
bewaqoof nahi dekha tere jaisa.

aadhe ganje 
adhe rapper
adhi shakti 
adhi mehnat
kaise sun lu 
kyu lu seh kar
kaun behtar
you know better

muhfaad kare muh pe blabber
rate hue sabke pattern
tu hi monseure tu hi madam
wig laga ke lagte karen

chidhta hai to chidhta reh
mai to karu daya na
kauwa kha ke goo
kis muh se bane sayana?

bat suno bhaijaan
muh pe maru paaydaan
faltu jo khaye kaan
to sareaam fir trahimam

leta kaun tujhe serious
get ready for veer ras
banda nahi tu gimmick 
Mr. idiot on periods.
chahye nahi opinion
mai 16 se nahi lenient
karu break character tera 
lo so that you can be real

ye koi beef wala nyauta nahi
tujhe bhaunkne se roka nahi
yad dilau doodh chhati ka par
hazam tujhe hoga nahi
soongh bagle aur kachhiyan
tu aur kisi jogga nahi
likhne se chutkule 
muqabla hoga nahi.

tere jaisi thuki mile
road pe baleno
mai bas dikhta hu akela
aake maarte hai teeno
mere jaise likhna hai to 
lagenge maheeno 
tujhe koi bhi na dhoondhe
agar hota bhi tu nemo

firse chadha bali 
haththe UP wale ke
tere area ke laundo
ko duty baatenge
ise sapno ki duniya se kheech ke laao
sare aate jate bulbul ko chooti katenge

apas ke mazak mat la screen pe
yahan baksha nahi kisi ko maine scene me
ye goat kya hai puchhte hai memne
bhosdi ke sote ke de dunga neend me.
